{
  "translationLines": [
    {
      "lineNumber": 128971,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「まったく、油断も隙もない奴め。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Good grief, not a moment's carelessness or slip-up.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 128972,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　散れ、散れ」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Scatter, scatter.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 128973,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「はい……」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Yes...\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 128974,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「かなみさん、大丈夫ですか？",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Kanami-san, are you okay?\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 128975,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　罠で足が痛むなら私ヒーリングを……」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "If your foot hurts from the trap, I can heal you...\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 128976,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「あ、あの、あ、シィルちゃん、",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Ah, um, ah, Siiru-chan,\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 128977,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　私、ごめんね、ごめんね……」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"I'm sorry, I'm sorry...\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 128978,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「へ？」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Huh?\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 128979,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「あうあう、恋人だなんだって調子に乗って……",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Auu auu, getting carried away saying you're lovers and all...\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 128980,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　シィルちゃんがいるのに、私……」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Even though Siiru-chan is here, I...\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 128981,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「あ、いえ、そんな……！",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Ah, no, that's not it...!\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 128982,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　私なんてランス様の奴隷ですし……」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "I'm just Lord Rance's slave after all...\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 128983,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「それにランス様にお子さんが増えていたり、",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Besides, Lord Rance has had more children, and\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 128984,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　リア様やマジックさんは妊娠していたりで……」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Lady Ria and Magic-san are pregnant, and...\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 128985,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「なんだかもう、",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Somehow already,\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 128986,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　ショックを受ける暇もなくって……」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "I haven't even had time to be shocked...\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 128987,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「あ、良ければ、お弁当食べて下さい。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Ah, if you'd like, please eat the bento.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 128988,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　お腹、空いてるんですよね」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "You're hungry, right?\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 128989,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「うう……シィルちゃん……」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Ugh... Siiru-chan...\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 128990,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「……私が港で貴方が船で、ね」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"...I at the port, you on the ship, right?\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 128991,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「シィルちゃんって心広いのねぇ……ﾇﾇﾇ」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Siiru-chan, you really have a generous heart... *nunu*\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 128992,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「違う違う。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"No, no.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 128993,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　実はシィルちゃんが一番贅沢な願い事があるから、",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Actually Siiru-chan has the most extravagant wish,"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 128994,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　かなみちゃんに怒る権利ないって考えてるのよ」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "so I think she has no right to be mad at Kanami-chan.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 128995,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「……それと多少は自覚もあるのかしらね。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"...Maybe she’s a little aware of that too.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 128996,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　そうそう捨てられないって」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"That she just can't be so easily discarded.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 128997,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「え、あら、なに？",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Eh, oh, what is it?\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 128998,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　ランス君やっぱりああ見えて、",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Lance-kun, despite appearances,\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 128999,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　実はシィルちゃんのことそうなの？　ﾇﾇﾇ」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"is actually like that about Siiru-chan? *nunu*\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 129000,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「そりゃ、ね。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Well, yeah.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 129001,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　見ての通りよ」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"As you can see.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 129002,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「あらあらあら、まあまあまあ。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Oh my, oh my, oh my, well well well.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 129003,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　んふふふ、そうなのそうなの。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Hehehe, yes yes.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 129004,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　へーーー、ふーーん。ﾇﾇﾇ」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Heeey, hmmm. *nunu*\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 129005,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「なんだ、お前ら。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"What’s with you guys?\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 129006,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　井戸端会議する主婦みたいだぞ。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"You're like housewives gossiping by the well.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 129007,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　なんの話をしてる？」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"What are you talking about?\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 129008,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「なーんでもないのよ〜ん。ﾇﾇﾇ」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"It’s nothing at all~~. *nunu*\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 129009,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「なんでもないのよ」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"It's really nothing.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 129010,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「？？？」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"???\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 129011,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「まあいいや。かなみ、",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Whatever. Kanami,\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 129012,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　お前もパーティーに入って",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"you join the party too,"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 129013,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　俺様の為にキリキリと働くのだ」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"and work hard for me.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 129014,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「う、うん、分かった」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Y-yeah, got it.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 129015,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「頑張るから見ててね、ランス」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"I'll do my best, so watch me, Lance.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 129016,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "シィルとロッキーとかなみが",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Siiru, Rocky, and Kanami"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 129017,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "メガワスと話していた。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "were talking with Megawas."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 129018,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「ええ、そんな大昔からだすか！？",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Eh, from such a long time ago!?\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 129019,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「ええ、私達ホルスがこの惑星に来たのは、",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Yes, the Hols came to this planet"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 129020,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　もう何千年も昔の話よ。ﾇﾇﾇ」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "thousands of years ago. *nunu*\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 129021,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「私達は別の惑星からやってきた移民団だったの。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"We were an immigrant group from another planet."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 129022,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　その数は一万人。ﾇﾇﾇ」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Their number was ten thousand. *nunu*\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 129023,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「一万人……",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Ten thousand...\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 129024,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　なんだかおら、クラクラしてきただす……」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Somehow, I’m getting dizzy...\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 129025,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「あ、では、今もここに",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Ah, so even now here,"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 129026,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　それくらいの数の方々が……」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "there are about that many people...?\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 129027,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "メガワスはゆっくりと首を横に振った。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Megawas slowly shook his head."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 129028,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「この惑星には事故で墜落したんだけど、",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"We crashed on this planet by accident,"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 129029,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　そのとき運悪く、ね……ﾇﾇﾇ」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "and unfortunately at that time... *nunu*\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 129030,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「宇宙を移動中はコールドスリープ装置で",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"During space travel, we were in cold sleep devices"
    }
  ]
}

